rComments: Once you get to know halls, you'll realize how bitter, out of touch and antisocial he is. You need a teacher to connect with and not a talking textbook. What a waist of a great mind, to think he will pass on nothing but pessimism and shallowness of character and integrity. Good luck to you all future students. ADVICE: stay a stray from this bag
AHHH! I love him! He's awesome and is so into Earth Science, you gotta love this man.

I'm not much of a scientific person, but his classes were easy to understand, and he's very funny.  He did a lot of experiments and stuff in front of the class.  It would have been perfect if it hadn't been so early!!!
The only other prof I know who's more into the course he's teaching than Steve Engels. GREAT explainer, makes everything *interesting*. Funny guy too! Sounds kinda like Frasier Crane!
ol' shooter.. real nice. too much info in his lectures to write down. knows all!
